<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('../layouts/header.ejs'); %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/produk.css">
    <title>AsdarrID - Genshin Impact</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../layouts/none.ejs'); %>
    <%- include('../layouts/navbar.ejs'); %>

    <!-- konten -->
    <div class="single-product py-5" onclick="closeRightMenu()">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-4 order-lg-last">
                    <article>
                        <div class="card border-0 mb-4">
                            <div class="card-body p-0" style="background-color: #f8fafd;">

                                <!-- nama produk & logo -->
                                <div class="d-flex gap-3 align-items-center" style="justify-content: left!important;">
                                    <div class="thumbnail-product">
                                        <img itemprop="image" src="assets/images/game/genshin-impact.webp" alt=""
                                            class="rounded-3" height="100px">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="product-data">
                                        <h1 class="fs-5 mb-1 entry-title" itemprop="name">Genshin Impact</h1>
                                        <div class="fs-6 text-muted">HoYoverse</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- end -->

                                <!-- app/play store & situs web -->
                                <div class="product_link_store">
                                    <div class="item_link_store">
                                        <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.miHoYo.GenshinImpact"
                                            target="_blank">
                                            <img src="assets/images/logo/play.svg"
                                                title="Temukan di Google Playstore" />
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="item_link_store">
                                        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id1517783697" target="_blank">
                                            <img src="assets/images/logo/apps.svg" title="Download di App Store" />
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="item_link_store">
                                        <a href="https://genshin.hoyoverse.com/en/"
                                            class="item_link_website d-flex gap-2 align-items-center" target="_blank"
                                            title="Situs WEB">
                                            <img src="assets/images/game/genshin-impact.webp" class="rounded-circle">
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="mb-0">SITUS</span>
                                                <p class="mb-0">WEB</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- end -->

                                <!-- deskripsi produk -->
                                <div class="mt-2">
                                    <span>
                                        <h5 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span
                                                style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><b>
                                                    Tentang Genshin Impact</b></span></h5>
                                        <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span
                                                style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">
                                                Teyvat, sebuah dunia fantasi yang bebas, dinamis, dan penuh dengan
                                                kehidupan mistis, dunia di mana tujuh elemen yang saling mengalir,
                                                berpadu, menari dan beradu.

                                                Pemain berperan sebagai seorang dari sepasang saudara kembar yang
                                                berkelana dari dunia satu ke dunia lain.<span id="dots">...</span><span
                                                    id="more"> Sampai sesosok dewa yang tak
                                                    dikenal menghadang langkahmu, merenggut saudara kembarmu, dan
                                                    menyegel
                                                    kekuatanmu. Karena sihirnya, kamu tertidur tak sadarkan diri.

                                                    Saat kesadaranmu kembali, dunia di sekelilingmu. bukan lagi dunia
                                                    yang
                                                    kamu kenal
                                                </span>
                                        </p>
                                        <div>
                                        </div>
                                    </span>
                                    <a onclick="myFunction()" id="myRead"> Read more </a>
                                </div>
                                <!-- end -->
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- cara top up -->
                        <div class="card product-how-to-top-up">
                            <h6> Cara Top Up </h6>
                            <div class="card-body p-3">
                                <div class="fs-6" style="font-size: 0.89rem;">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Masukkan User ID</li>
                                        <li>Pilih Nominal Genesis Crystal</li>
                                        <li>Pilih Metode Pembayaran</li>
                                        <li>Tulis nomor WhatsApp yang benar!</li>
                                        <li>Klik Beli & lakukan Pembayaran</li>
                                        <li>Upload bukti pembayaran</li>
                                        <li> Genesis Crystal akan masuk otomatis ke akun Anda.</li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- end -->
                    </article>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-8">
                    <form>
                        <div class="card border-0 cbm-section-shadow mb-4 product-form-input-order">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2" style="justify-content: left!important;">
                                    <div class="number-form">1</div>
                                    <h4 class="mb-0 ms-2 fw-600">Masukkan User ID</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row g-3">
                                    <div class="col-8">
                                        <label class="form-label" for="userID">User ID</label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="userID" id="userID"
                                            placeholder="Masukan User ID">
                                        <small class="where-my-user-id" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                                            data-bs-target="#WhereMyUserID">Dimana User ID Saya?</small>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-4">
                                        <label class="form-label" for="server">server</label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="server" id="server"
                                            placeholder="server">
                                        <small class="where-my-user-id" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                                            data-bs-target="#WhereMyServer">Dimana Server Saya?</small>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Dimana User ID Saya? -->
                                    <div class="modal fade" id="WhereMyUserID" aria-labelledby="WhereMyUserIDLabel">
                                        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                                            <div class="modal-content">
                                                <div class="modal-header">
                                                    <div class="modal-title">
                                                        <div class="d-flex flex-row align-items-center">
                                                            <div class="fw-bold">Dimana User ID Saya?</div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                                        aria-label="Close"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="modal-body">
                                                    <img src="assets/images/game/id/gensin01.jpg"
                                                        alt="Dimana User ID Saya?">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="modal-footer">
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary"
                                                        data-bs-dismiss="modal">Tutup</button>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <!-- end -->

                                    <!-- Dimana Server Saya? -->
                                    <div class="modal fade" id="WhereMyServer" aria-labelledby="WhereMyServerLabel">
                                        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                                            <div class="modal-content">
                                                <div class="modal-header">
                                                    <div class="modal-title">
                                                        <div class="d-flex flex-row align-items-center">
                                                            <div class="fw-bold">Dimana Server Saya?</div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                                        aria-label="Close"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="modal-body">
                                                    <img src="assets/images/game/id/gensin02.png"
                                                        alt="Dimana User ID Saya?">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="modal-footer">
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary"
                                                        data-bs-dismiss="modal">Tutup</button>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <!-- end -->
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card border-0 cbm-section-shadow mb-4 bg-white rounded-5 product-form-input-order">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3" style="justify-content: left!important;">
                                    <div class="number-form">2</div>
                                    <h4 class="mb-0 ms-2 fw-600">Pilih Jumlah Genesis Crystal</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">

                                    <div class="row row-cols-3 g-3">

                                        <!-- 70 -->
                                        <div class="col mt-3">
                                            <div class="list-group">
                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check h-100" name="denom" id="nominal-70"
                                                    autocomplete="off">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-info " style="height:50%;width:100%"
                                                    for="nominal-70">70 Crystal</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <!-- end -->

                                        <!-- 140 -->
                                        <div class="col mt-3">
                                            <div class="list-group">
                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check h-100" name="denom"
                                                    id="nominal-140" autocomplete="off">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-info" for="nominal-140">140
                                                    Crystal</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <!-- end -->

                                        <!-- 355 -->
                                        <div class="col mt-3">
                                            <div class="list-group">
                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check h-100" name="denom"
                                                    id="nominal-355" autocomplete="off">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-info" for="nominal-355">355
                                                    Crystal</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <!-- end -->

                                        <!-- 720 -->
                                        <div class="col mt-3">
                                            <div class="list-group">
                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="denom" id="nominal-720"
                                                    autocomplete="off">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-info" for="nominal-720">720
                                                    Crystal</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <!-- end -->

                                        <!-- 1450 -->
                                        <div class="col mt-3">
                                            <div class="list-group">
                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="denom" id="nominal-1450"
                                                    autocomplete="off">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-info" for="nominal-1450">1450
                                                    Crystal</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <!-- end -->

                                        <!-- 2180 -->
                                        <div class="col mt-3">
                                            <div class="list-group">
                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="denom" id="nominal-2180"
                                                    autocomplete="off">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-info" for="nominal-2180">2180
                                                    Crystal</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <!-- end -->
                                    </div>


                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <%- include('../layouts/list-pembayaran.ejs'); %>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- end konten -->

    <%- include('../layouts/footer.ejs'); %>
    <script src="assets/js/button.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>